{
  "name": "RPlog_Left_Unsaid",
  "title": "What Went Unsaid",
  "summary": "Over a quiet shipboard dinner aboard a New Republic vessel orbiting Mon Calamari, Jedi Master Luke Skywalker and his student Sabrina linger over Alderaanian wine after Leia is called away. Their easy reminiscing about youth and family slowly drifts toward an unspoken attraction neither feels free to name. When Sabrina, loosened by the wine, nearly confesses her feelings, Luke recoils into his role as her teacher and resolves to keep his distance, rising to leave. Though she finds the courage to stop him and lays her heart bare, he insists their bond cannot be what she wishes, leaving her crushed. She gathers the wine bottle and walks away alone, the feeling between them left painfully unresolved.",
